snippet.textDisplay:
Heya boys, 4wder from CA, USA here.. And a Toyota fan. Strangely enough, also a huge fan of yours, as well. Funniest moments of 2019 are as follows: 1. Anytime Graham gets hit in the coconuts. 2. The juxtaposition of emotion between Rocket and Ash as they go up that gnarly hill. Rocket having the time of his life as Ash defecates himself is hysterically funny. 3. I guess Shauno's attempts at fishing are pretty funny, too. 4. Shauno nearly blowing chunks after every stinky boghole never fails to amuse. Anyway, keep up the good work, I'm green with envy not being in the Aussie bush somewhere.
P.S. Best of luck with your current wildfire situation. As a Californian I know how much it sucks to see the places you love go up in smoke.
Cheers!! 🍻
